{"tid":1554093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"舉報警隊觸犯刑事罪行","createTime":"2019-09-09T00:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T00:32:59.000Z","uid":279102,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33aa17ef4e6d3461c7b75d7ce5720589aeec2425","tid":1554093,"uid":279102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:05:12.000Z","msg":"香港特別行政區行政首長、林鄭月娥女士和警務處處長、盧偉聰：<br />\n<br />\n我現在向你們舉報警務人員於 2019 年 9 月 7 日在香港鐵路大埔墟站向人群作出無合理辯解的襲擊／攻擊，涉嫌觸犯刑事罪行之圖造成身體嚴重傷害而射擊、企圖射擊、傷人或打人(s.17 ca 212)， 4.2 傷人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害(s.19 cap 212)， 4.3 襲擊致造成身體傷害(s.39 cap 212)， 4.4 普通襲擊(s.40 cap 212)， 4.5 在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器 (s.33 cap 245)。<br />\n<br />\n我初步認為涉案人士有特首林鄭月娥女士、警務處處長盧偉聰、副警務處處長鄧炳強、新界南總區指揮官陶輝、沙田區指揮官麥劉慧敏女士、現場指揮官、直接揮動警棒打人那些警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n請告訴給我相關的報案編號，以便作為跟進用途。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我建立網頁 <a href=\"http://www.hkscandal.com/policecrime190907taipo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkscandal.com%2Fpolicecrime190907taipo.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=7fa8b364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkscandal.com/policecrime190907taipo.html</a> 讓全民協助我跟進這宗案件。 以後其他案件也用這個格式來跟進。<br />\n<br />\nNOW 電視和中大校園電台總編輯：<br />\n<br />\n在網頁 <a href=\"http://www.hkscandal.com/policecrime190907taipo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkscandal.com%2Fpolicecrime190907taipo.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=7fa8b364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkscandal.com/policecrime190907taipo.html</a> 我借用你們的片段作為我舉報刑事罪行用途。如果你們反對，請通知我，讓我盡快移除。<br />\n<br />\n何超光<br />\n香港一位最卑微的小市民<br />\n<br />\n副本抄送：多個 whatsapp 群組<br />\n                  facebook / 司法與法治 群組<br />\n                  facebook / 法治毒瘤 - 警察  群組<br />\n                  連登 討論區<br />\n                  facebook / 巴打絲打 facebook club<br />\n                  數個連儂牆"},{"pid":"f5ebf905bf9e1e3ef50ff4d3a7c3f20b9854caa6","tid":1554093,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9fe0c454aeaf584112df4e8141d4ae93b0eece","tid":1554093,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:19:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dab746adfbb5738e89708bea3d1792256d7be5ec","tid":1554093,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4416baa5355917e7f262e55b4c6ad22d85bc9da8","tid":1554093,"uid":291653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:32:59.000Z","msg":"推~~"}]}